column9: SEED-STAGE • LOGISTICS TECH • FOR-PROFIT • SOCIAL PURPOSE CORPORATION. For buyers and sellers of perishable goods, Transparent Path creates real-time, end-to-end supply chain visibility technologies that reduce waste, cost, and risk.  WHO WE ARE: Former senior executives from the food, tech, and social impact sectors, from companies like Amazon, IBM, Xerox, Microsoft, Target, and General Mills. We came together in 2020 to use the skills we honed over long careers to create meaningful positive impacts. Our social mission: to keep food, medicines and other critical perishables out of landfills.  Founded as an LLC in 2018. Restructured and launched as a social purpose corp (C-corp) in 2020.  PROBLEM Supply chain data technologies have been underfunded for generations — still largely powered by paper, faxes and disconnected systems. These antiquated approaches were incapable of handling the enormous systemic strains caused by pandemic-related labor and equipment shortages, disruptions, and growing, complex regulation. Paper systems mean shippers and receivers can't manage what they can't see. So we decided to combine a number of advanced technologies and new approaches for today's challenges, including AI, IoT, 5G, printed electronics, and machine vision. SOLUTIONS We bring both software and hardware solutions to the market to reduce cost, waste, and risk in perishable supply chains.  -- PRODUCT 1: The Transparent Path Visibility Platform (PaaS). Customers affix our continuously-connected cellular sensors to pallets entering the supply chain. These sensors constantly capture and report the location, temperature, humidity, and other factors for these shipments into our visibility cloud. This platform was built with collaboration in mind. Supply chain partners are grouped in Consortiums — dynamic partnerships based around common trade relationships. Product customers are tracked, easing data sharing and showing who's "got the ball."  When location or conditions jeopardize our customers' products, we send out real-time alerts to the appropriate parties who can intervene and save the shipment, along with its freshness, safety, and financial value.  -- PRODUCT 2: FreshScore™ - our patented predictive freshness algorithm targeted at buyers. FreshScore uses both production data and supply chain environmental data to predict the freshness of perishables before they arrive at retail. This unique algorithm arms food producers with quality control data, allowing for the routing of the best product to the best customers, minimizing surprises and rejections. It also helps reduce waste by anticipating freshness and viability issues before they occur. We are partnering with ReFED, the top food waste non-profit, to bring this technology to market. -- PRODUCT 3: ProofScore™ - our "credit score for transparency." ProofScore is a patented algorithm that scores perishable producers and products based on data transparency. The more data shared with supply chain partners and consumers, the higher the ProofScore.  ProofScore puts information into the hands of consumers, answering the question, where did this product come from? How did it get to me? What happened to it along the way? ProofScore-ranked products can command higher margins and grow stronger customer satisfaction. We are partnering with a large Japanese multinational firm on its development.  -- PRODUCT 4: ProofTracker - our eco-friendly sensor device. This advanced temperature/humidity/shock tracker is a cellular gateway built on biodegradable materials.    BENEFITS Our products reduce customers' supply chain losses, retailer rejections, insurance premiums, wasted time, and labor costs spent on reconciliations. They also reduce negative impacts to natural capital, including keeping food and perishables out of landfills. Using our system, all supply chain partners know exactly what's happening to products in transit — reducing disputes while improving collaboration and trust. And customer relationships are maximized by the delivery of fresh, safe products at full margin.  CUSTOMER PROFILE Transparent Path technologies support food, pharmaceuticals, blood/plasma, transplant organs, and construction chemical shipments. The company also currently provides asset tracking for high-end hard goods.  PARTNERSHIPS Transparent Path has created partnerships with Intel, T-Mobile, Duke University, and ReFED. Intel has donated hardware, software, and ongoing counsel since 2020. We are working with Second Sun Laboratories to develop the most advanced hardware in the market, and with a large multinational Japanese tech manufacturer to develop ProofScore.  ACCELERATORS/INCUBATORS Over its short tenure, Transparent Path has been accepted into numerous accelerators, including 5G Open Innovation Lab, Microsoft for Startups, NewChip, and most recently, Plug and Play IoT.  FUNDRAISING To date, Transparent Path has been funded via bootstrapping, two RegCF raises, three grants, and four angel investors. In April 2023, the company was awarded grants totaling $440,000 from the National Science Foundation, ReFED, and the State of Washington. The company is building traction toward a Series A that will fund sales scaling and feature expansion.   FOR MORE INFORMATION Headquartered in the US, Transparent Path was founded by Eric Weaver, a 30-year enterprise transformation specialist. Prior to founding the company, Weaver launched the Xerox Customer Experience Practice, where he managed a $550M services book of business. His executive team includes senior leaders from Amazon, General Mills, Microsoft, Target, KraftHeinz, Xerox PARC, and the University of California at Berkeley.  Please visit transparentpath.com to learn more.

column9: At KwikTrust we've built two unusual products. The first is KwikSign - a digital signature app, which doesn't sound particularly innovative but we've approached the problem from a different angle. Our vision of the future is that people won't want to just sign contracts. There are new problems to be solved. They will need to sign any asset to either prove that they own it, approve it, agree with it, or want to protect it. This could be any asset type - contracts, video, audio, designs, drawings, deeds, code and more. In an age of artificial intelligence and fake information it's more important than ever to validate the authenticity of any asset. We achieve this by enabling any file type to be checked, validated, signed and recorded on a blockchain thereby creating a tamperproof record. Everything that is created can be linked to the validated identity of the validators to prove it is true and original. What are the use cases for this? There are many - creating deeds of ownership, issuing stock or share certificates, carrying out due diligence, recording intellectual property, confirming that a video, photo or audio file is the true and original version, in fact creating a tamperproof record of any event or asset. Our second product, launching next month, takes this one step further. Once an asset is created it needs to be transferable, tradable and traceable. To solve this problem we have built a SuperNFT which is an asset linked to the validated identities of the creators or legal owners. Because the SuperNFT 'knows' who its owners are it is also a mechanism for collecting and disbursing monies to the rightful beneficiaries, and it does this Super-quickly. Our first foray is in the world of music to enable artists to create new experiences for their audiences and to enable artists to be paid more quickly and more accurately.

column9: Imagine an A.I assistant that can find someone qualified to take care of your problem, get an estimated price for the service, and give you a few start times to choose from.  Does this conversation sound familiar? I have this problem at ZIP code 39531. Can you fix it, when can you fix it and how much will it cost? Our A.I replies to that request with answers to each part. Example service request: “39531 toilet won’t flush” Example A.I assistant reply: Service Name: Toilet Repair (Won't Flush, Running, Clog) Estimated Price: $85 Soonest Arrival Window: 10/18 Thur, 9:00am-10:00am Click here to order this service Or find similar services here  Hometown Workforce is like DoorDash for services with an A.I assistant that helps consumers hire service providers. These people create a series of service listings on our marketplace. Consumers then pick the service they need, choose an available start time, and deposit 1% of the estimated total down. This 1% contractually obligates the person to show up on time and complete the work for the price estimated. If they don't they risk losing access to the platform.  This order process also runs the person's entire business. It manages payments, provides jobs, and schedules those jobs. All the person has to do is show up on time and do a good job. In exchange for this commitment to being honest and reliable, our tech can turn the skills of virtually anyone regardless of race, gender, background, or circumstances into a successful business. Angie's List and all the other lead gen sites do one thing. They connect consumers with contractors. They can't schedule the job. They can't verify the quality of work and they can't verify the price is fair. Without all 4 you can't effectively help consumers complete jobs. We take care of all 4 and more! MISSION STATEMENT: Our mission is to help eliminate poverty by turning people's skills into successful businesses. This is the first true solution to poverty I'm aware of. It's also perhaps the most powerful tool ever conceived for incentivizing people to be honest and reliable.  HOW OUR TECHNOLOGY WORKS: What makes this platform truly revolutionary is the series of listings people create on our marketplace. These listings pre-price and pre-timed their individual services.  Since each service is pre-priced we can standardize prices which eliminates price gouging, it also ensures the person gets paid.  Since each service is pre-timed the consumer can look at the person's work calendar and see all the available openings with enough hours to accommodate the specific job. Then they pick one which ensures the person shows up on time. It also provides them with jobs and manages every hour of every day. It tells the person where to go, what to do, and when to be there. There are billions of ordinary people who have skills people will pay for. They just have no idea how to turn those skills into a successful business. That’s exactly what Hometown Workforce does! We also have a training division that can provide people with skills. You choose a trade, we partner you with an instructor who will create listings specific to your career path. Consumers order those services and after you learn to do the work on the job. All the listings are turned over to you and instantly you have a successful business. Order services today: www.wfskills.com

column9: Worddio is an AI-driven vocabulary-building app. We are growing our user base at a rapid pace because we offer our customers: - The unique feature to learn words without touching their smartphone. - 34 languages that cover 90% of the world's population. Our in-house AI/ML models help us in: - Building individual learning paths. - Optimizing marketing costs. - Deep user database segmentation (psychological, behavioral, and interests based) Customer Problem The main problem we face is the language barrier between peoples. This specifically applies to EU as a multi-lingual community. From other hand the biggest challenge for learning a foreign language is time. Advanced online technologies provide many learning opportunities but all of them require 100% focus for a long period of time which many people do not have. Products & Services To solve this problem, we turned the flashcards that students often use to memorize words into audio flashcards. Over 2000 people say that Worddio is a great tool for learning new words. With Worddio you can learn new words on the move or while doing something else, without touching your phone. Through this method, the learner will also memorize the pronunciation in the correct way, spoken by a native language speaker. We safe students time! Target Market The Worddio app is designed specifically for people learning a foreign language and who don't have time to learn and memorize new words. The Global Online Language Learning Market was valued at $12.49 billion in 2019 and is projected to reach $25.73 billion by 2027. With its 34 languages Worddio has potential usefulness for over 90% of the world population. Does it work? We have more than 200K installations and more than 1300 paying users. Business Model - subscriptions: 1, 3, 6 and 12 months, lifetime - up-sales of premium content - advanced flashcards by topics, Audiobooks and Podcasts. - Ads - general or targeted based on user profiles - Apply data & technology to other platforms/apps/fields . . . Developing a B2C model on a global level takes time and resources to break even, but once that happens, the return on investment is maximized at scale. Customer Segments Professionals: adults looking to improve their foreign-language skills for business or career reasons Casual learners: travelers, expats, or other persons wishing to learn a new language or enhance their current knowledge Sector-specific: Service workers, such as call-center staff or healthcare workers, who can perform better with a larger vocabulary and accurate pronunciation. Youth: 12-20 year-olds studying secondary languages in schools Sales & Marketing Strategy We have technology that allows us to build psychological profiles and predict users' behaviours without accessing their sensitive data. We can build bespoke learning paths, custom sales funnels, and target ads. The data gathered allow the pursue of three main objectives: optimzing marketing resources by leveraging predictive machine learning models creating individual learning paths based on users needs upsale of particular content or products Competitors The language learning apps space looks crowded but in fact there is a specific empty niche - passive learning. There are a lot of language learning apps on the market, but none of them use a passive learning method to save time for their users - Worddio is the only one that does. We are opening a new market group to support language learning. The Worddio app is a pseudo-passive learning app powered by AI which saves student time. Competitive Advantage Worddio main advantages are: - our app’s passive learning method  - huge stock of professionally recorded audio-flashcards in 34 languages. - scientific-based approach that leverages ML and AI to optimize costs and improve user experience - premium content section - AI features that will help us deliver the ultimate hands-free experience to our users.

column9: Hannah Systems’ mission is to deliver open and anonymous traffic data, never utilizing personal information, bringing focus to the most important tasks at hand, reducing emissions, improving congestion, and ultimately changing the way we live. Hannah Systems is making a difference in a progressive and socially beneficial way and we are emphasizing this objective by becoming a Public Benefit Corp. Hannah is a B2B software company that creates openness and the democratization of data, free from the location-based advertising business model.  The Hannah Systems AI was developed by a team of PhDs and traffic engineers and provides detailed intersection data, resulting in a more comprehensive view of the city leading to less time spent in traffic.  At Hannah Systems we enhance traffic data with AI technology and share this anonymous data via our open data platform. This enriched information enables analysis of traffic patterns and pedestrian activity, and reduces travel time, pollution, and congestion. Hannah Systems’ enhanced data can help cities redesign light phasing and surface new routes that can genuinely improve travel times. Traffic information is the catalyst that can bring about change, however, data has become increasingly more personalized and is a protected and proprietorial asset that it is not being utilized to help our cities. The Hannah Systems detailed traffic information makes travel more efficient, reducing the stress and anxiety of city driving, reducing emissions and making roads safer. The Hannah Systems open data platform is the foundation for companies looking to improve pedestrian safety, reduce emissions, streamline traffic and address the needs of the AV industry. Hannah Systems is partnering with cities around the globe in order to deliver the next generation of open, anonymous, and ethically managed traffic data. Hannah provides a deep understanding of congestion problems through advanced analytics, microsimulation of every intersection, a macro view of the overall city and the Hannah Systems’ Traffic AI.

column9: Vocalto, a fully automated healthcare documentation tool, is returning humanity to medicine through the use of Artificial Intelligence.  Vocalto uses Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning to parse a conversation between a patient and their physician and create a transcript.  From this transcript, Vocalto creates a recognizable SOAP note based on the conversation.  Finally, Vocalto parses the information in the transcript and sends Medications, Allergies, Diagnoses and other data directly into the physicians Electronic Medical Record for storage.  Automating physician documentation is posed to remove dozens of documentation hours from physicians each week and bring back back the face-to-face interaction that both physicians and patients crave.

column9: MedlyticsAi is standardizing data for all healthcare systems to enable interoperability & precision health.  We believe patients should be at the center of healthcare and support the industry’s transition to a value-based-care system.  We're helping to bridge the gap between disparate health systems & their inability to streamline systematic communication of health data; to achieve better patient outcomes and increase human longevity.  How do we do this? Our solution’s ability to query patient information, significantly faster and much more accurate than any front-end API, will help physicians reduce the time spent looking at a computer screen.  We do the hard work on the back-end, so physicians can do the critical work on the front-end; providing a high efficacy driven & personalized care approach.   How do we do this? MedlyticsAi’s population health management platform leverages natural language processing , natural language understanding, machine learning, and other technological innovations; improving hospital workflow & enabling each physician to see, on average, 3 more patients per day/11.4hr work shift.  We do this by significantly reducing the time spent on EHR chart review, which also helps to reduce physician burnout.  The ability to transform existing health care data into the new standard (FHIR), will spark innovation and yield better patient outcomes.  Our technology is strategically built to implement and comply with the standards set forth by Health level 7,   FHIR v4.0.1, and the US Core Implementation Guide v3.1.0. We understand FHIR guidelines will continue to improve as we collectively journey on this endeavor.  Thus, we are fully committed to monitoring, understanding, and quickly implementing improved updates to adhere to these evolving guidelines.  Results are achieved through action.  We analogize compliment pairings like theory and practical application, to depict  interoperability and MedlyticsAi.

column9: Think of Sidekick Ai as your smart scheduling assistant. Our platform offers multiple ways to schedule meetings including; forward to schedule, link sharing and sidekick scheduling. We are the first scheduling software that uses machine learning to process language to schedule a meeting.  Forward to Schedule: When you receive an email, simply forward this email to your Sidekick. Sidekick will then read the email and try to find requested dates and time from the sender and match it with your schedule. If it missing information, it will reply back to the sender and coordinate the meeting for you.  Link Sharing: This is pretty standard in today's scheduling softwares. Simply share your scheduling link with someone and they will chat with your Sidekick to schedule the meeting with you.  Sidekick Scheduling:  Here is where more magic happens. Simply request that Sidekick schedule a meeting for you and it's done. Tell Sidekick who you want to meet with and when. From there, Sidekick will email the invitees and find times that work for everyone and get something scheduled for everyone. You don't have to worry about coordinating, following up or finding times... that is what Sidekick is for.  Sidekick also offers auto scheduling with your closest of contacts. We allow users to turn on auto scheduling for close contacts and when you want to schedule a meeting, it's instantly done and will be added to everyone's calendars.

column9: CrunchMetrics is an advanced anomaly detection system, that leverages the combined power of statistical methods and AI-ML based techniques to sift through your data to identify incidents that are business critical in nature. It examines historical data to understand and establish what is ‘normal’ behavior, and then constantly monitors data streams to single out ‘abnormal’ patterns, known as anomalies. Identified incidents are flagged in real-time, enabling stakeholders to act instantly, and thereby minimizing the potential impact on the business.

column9: Amicus Brain Innovations, Inc. is a NY-based digital health startup focused on bringing the power of Artificial Intelligence (AI) technology to transform caring for patients with neurodegenerative disorders.  As a woman-owned small business, our company is known for it values, diversity, inclusion and parity.  Even as an early stage startup, we walk the talk with women engineers making up more than 50% of our technical workforce.  The number of people in the US living with cognitive impairment (including Alzheimer’s Disease and related dementia) is over 5.8M today and is expected to increase to nearly 14M by 2050. The rapidly growing population of informal caregivers (more than 16M today) of people with cognitive impairment is subject to high stress due to patient behavioral symptoms, increased demands on caregiver time, and lack of adequate care-giving knowledge to address changing patient conditions. Caregivers face depleted income due to reduced productivity, higher use of health care services, decreased quality of life, higher burnout and risk of earlier mortality. The economic value of the caregivers' time spent providing more than 8.5 billion hours of care is estimated to be nearly $234 billion.   Amicus Brain’s AI-led services focus on caregivers and their patients before, during and after diagnosis, and while living with the disease, providing a scalable, cost-effective solution that reduces the caregiver load, raises the standard of current practices in neurodegenerative care and leads to improved health outcomes.

column9: Company Description: At Flexible Vision Inc., we are pioneering the future of manufacturing with our cutting-edge AI machine vision solutions. We specialize in the development of both hardware and software that empowers factory floors to reach new heights of efficiency, productivity, and quality. With a relentless commitment to innovation, we're redefining the way factories operate, making them smarter, faster, and more reliable than ever before. Our Vision: Our vision is to transform the manufacturing landscape by harnessing the power of artificial intelligence and computer vision. We believe that technology should enhance the capabilities of the workforce, not replace it. Through our AI machine vision solutions, we aim to create a seamless fusion of human expertise and machine precision, creating a synergy that optimizes the entire production process. What Sets Us Apart: - End-to-End Solutions: We offer a comprehensive suite of AI machine vision products that cover every aspect of the manufacturing process. From quality control and defect detection to process optimization and predictive maintenance, we provide a one-stop solution for our clients. - Innovation and Customization: We understand that every factory is unique. That's why we prioritize innovation and customization, tailoring our solutions to meet the specific needs and challenges of each manufacturing facility. - Hardware Excellence: Our state-of-the-art hardware components are designed and engineered for durability and reliability in industrial settings, ensuring that our systems perform flawlessly on the factory floor. - Scalability: Whether you're a small manufacturing operation or a large-scale facility, our solutions are designed to scale with your needs, ensuring you're always prepared for growth and evolution. - Human-Centric Approach: We don't just focus on machines; we prioritize the well-being and expertise of the people working in the factory. Our technology is designed to augment their capabilities, making their work safer, more engaging, and more valuable. Industries We Serve: Our AI machine vision technology is applicable across a wide range of industries, including but not limited to: - Automotive - Electronics - Aerospace - Pharmaceuticals - Food and Beverage - Consumer Goods - Energy - And more Join Us in Transforming Manufacturing: At Flexible Vision Inc., we're on a mission to lead the charge in transforming manufacturing into a more intelligent, efficient, and sustainable industry. We invite forward-thinkers, innovators, and problem-solvers to join us in this journey. Together, we'll shape the future of manufacturing with the power of AI machine vision, creating a world where quality, precision, and productivity go hand in hand.

column9: Geovea is a SaaS and AI-based web solution focused on simplifying travel discovery, planning, and booking processes for personal and business travelers, particularly those seeking local and unique experiences in North America. Geovea organizes travel in one place in the cloud, making it instantly searchable and available wherever the user goes. At the core, Geovea utilizes enhanced user map and route planning tools, allowing users to easily create simple or complex multi-destination trips. The platform also integrates industry-leading itinerary creation and calendar scheduling features to simplify any traveler’s trip experience.  One of its special offerings of Geovea is its Travel Chat AI. This AI-powered platform is revolutionizing the world of personalized travel planning by providing users with a fast and unparalleled experience in discovering and organizing their trips. Geovea Travel Chat AI allows users to easily tailor their search criteria at a city, state, or country level. It delivers personalized travel options in just 20 seconds, saving users time and effort and allowing them to discover hidden gems and off-the-beaten-path experiences. In summary, Geovea, through its mapping, itinerary, scheduling, and Travel Chat AI, is bringing a monumental shift in travel planning by enabling users to take complete control of their journey from start to finish. It allows for the exploration of exciting new destinations at unprecedented speeds, making the world of personalized travel more accessible and enjoyable. The bootstrapped startup company is based in Denver, Colorado, United States, and is now seeking its first round of seed funding to refine its platform and further leverage Geovea Travel Chat AI to provide the best user travel experience in the industry.

column9: LayerFive, a cross-device identity resolution platform, is changing how enterprises leverage their own consumer data.  While consumers are interacting with an enterprise using multiple devices and channels, enterprises are leveraging only a fraction of the consumer data to improve business outcome. The problem is that enterprises are having band-aid solutions to connect identities across various data sources due to the way technology has evolved. In the digital world, the problem becomes even more acute as consumers may not always be logged in while interacting with an enterprise, and typically use multiple devices.  LayerFive's innovative AI technology resolves cross-device digital identities in a privacy-safe first party data context across both logged-in and unknown consumers. column9: ColentAI is an innovative HR technology startup revolutionizing the way professional achievements and skills are recognized, managed, and utilized in the modern workforce. At its core, ColentAI aims to address the global skills gap that poses a significant challenge to efficient talent management and recruitment processes. This gap is primarily a result of the job market's rapid evolution, which traditional recruitment models and tools struggle to keep up with, leading to inefficiencies and missed opportunities. The flagship product of ColentAI, the "Colent Passport," is a digital platform designed as a comprehensive and dynamic ledger of professional skills. Unlike traditional resumes, which offer a static and often incomplete picture of a candidate's abilities and experiences, the Colent Passport provides a living, verified profile that evolves with each user's career journey. It integrates data from various sources, including project contributions, skill assessments, peer endorsements, and real-time work performance, to create a more accurate and holistic view of an individual's professional capabilities. ColentAI's mission is to facilitate a more efficient and effective connection between job seekers and employers. By leveraging advanced AI algorithms and a user-friendly interface, the platform ensures that companies can identify and recruit talent that precisely matches their needs, reducing the time and cost associated with hiring processes. For professionals, the Colent Passport offers a powerful tool to showcase their skills and achievements in a way that is verifiable and relevant to potential employers, thus enhancing their visibility and employability in a competitive job market. Founded by experts in recruitment and technology, ColentAI is poised to transform the recruitment landscape. Through its innovative approach and commitment to bridging the skills gap, ColentAI is not just a product but a movement towards creating a more efficient, inclusive, and future-ready global workforce.

column9: The world is experiencing Data Overload and Insights are highly interpretive and time sensitive. Critical decisions cannot wait for manual analysis to create contextual meaning from insights, they need to be automated to deliver decision guidance and Augmented Outcomes for Companies, Executives and Shareholders. Decision Point AI™ is the company that has an Augmented Intelligence Platform that facilitates Decisive Impact for Companies, Executives and Shareholders. It utilises Decision Science instead of Data Science to focus corporate efforts on critical and Augmented Outcomes to deliver Decisive Impact to its clients. Decision Point AI™ is vertical and horizontal Market agnostic and is focused on technology and consultancy services for any industry or organisation. Our Augmented Intelligence Platform is already in use in Government decision making and Decision Point is currently engaging with a number of commercial clients on their specific business cases. Decision Science Data driven decision making augmented intelligence #dddm_ai "Decision Point AI™ augmented intelligence supports decision making when there is a lack of data to otherwise make decisions" While the standard pathway for Decision Science is to focus on data as a tool to make decisions and solve business problems. Decision Point has further augmented the current thinking by adding collated data through an augmented intelligence platform and applying human interpretive algorithms that enable expert context to establish both true meaning and trajectory in a real time manner. Real time DDDM through Decision Point AI™ dddm_ai establishes a clear competitive advantage in a world where enterprises are told competitive advantage no longer exists DDDM_AI is fundamentally different from the slower data science route which is involved in finding insights by analysis and modelling from data, after this data has been collected, processed and structured by data engineer. While business who are "driven most by data-based decision making had 4% higher productivity rates and 5-6% higher profits, a study of 179 large publicly traded firms" by Brynjolfsson, Hitt and Kim of MIT Center for Digital Business found in 2011 based on Data Science. No impact analysis currently exist for the evolutionary real time DDDM_AI that utilises augmented intelligence but by extrapolation the expectation is for higher productivity, utilisation and profits for client companies. Subjective Logic Augmented Intelligence A fundamental aspect of the human condition is that nobody can ever determine with absolute certainty whether a proposition about the world is true or false. The human capacity to create theories or hunches can have profound impact on the direction and effectiveness of organisations, enterprise and countries. Decision Point utilises an Augmented Intelligence Platform built on subjective logic to refine and explicitly emphasise the factors and certainties that underwrite decision options. Additionally the Decision Point Augmented Intelligence Platform utilises human insights as part of its data queries to augment the processing power of the AI with context and meaning of that data through human knowledge and expertise. Subjective logic is a type of probabilistic logic that combines the capacity of probability theory to handle uncertainty with the capacity of deductive logic to exploit structure of formal argument. Subjective logic explicitly takes uncertainty and source data trust into account. Subjective logic is suitable for modelling and analysing situations involving uncertainty and relatively unreliable sources. Subjective logic can be used for modelling and analysing trust networks where a measurement of the degree to which one social actor (an individual or a group) trusts another social actor and Bayesian networks that represents a set of variables and their conditional dependencies via a directed acyclic graph (DAG). Bayesian networks are ideal for taking an event that occurred and predicting the likelihood that any one of several possible known causes was the contributing factor. For example, a Bayesian network could represent the probabilistic relationships between diseases and symptoms.

We use AI to enhance fitness instructors, not to replace them, because we believe it's time to put community back into community-based fitness. column9: INFXL's cloud service lets you train ultra-low power, fast, compact and inexpensive deep nets for battery-operated IoT edge devices and wearables. This service is focused on data from temperature, pressure, vibration, acceleration, speed, angular velocity, tilt, flow, smell, taste, and environmental sensors. The deep nets generated by this service work well on low-end hardware, but provide 10x the throughput of conventional nets on higher-end MCUs and FPGAs.  INFXL Cloud is targeted at those who want to use deep nets, but do not have the requisite knowledge and experience. A typical user will be an automation engineer, who knows how to collect and shape data and is interested in using deep nets as a controller. All you need to do is to normalize and scale the raw data and upload it in the form of features and labels files. Just two files; no questions asked about the deep net architecture or training parameters! In a day's time, you will receive a page of simple, highly-efficient C code that does not even read like a deep net. Adapt the input and output procedures to fit your project, and just like that, the system is good to go!

column9: E-CONCIERGE 2.0 is our innovative solution aimed at modernizing the home services industry. It's an intelligent virtual assistant, designed to streamline the often complex and time-consuming processes in the home service sector, beginning with the appliance repair industry. This smart bot excels at collecting a wealth of information in a user-friendly way. Through an interactive and intuitive Q&A process, E-CONCIERGE 2.0 engages with users to understand their needs, determine the nature of their service request, and schedule an appropriate service appointment. Not only does it replace manual scheduling and dispatching, but it also automates the process of adding the necessary information to the service provider's Google contacts and workflow management application, significantly reducing administrative workloads. As impressive as E-CONCIERGE 2.0 is, it's just the beginning of our vision. We're already setting our sights on the next iteration - E-CONCIERGE AI. This advanced version is envisaged to integrate AI capabilities to offer more than just streamlining scheduling and dispatching. E-CONCIERGE AI will be a game-changer in its ability to predict potential service issues before the technician arrives. Using the power of AI, it will process the collected information, anticipate the problem, and advise the technician on the necessary parts and procedures they might need. This predictive function will dramatically speed up service delivery by eliminating unnecessary guesswork. Beyond predictive troubleshooting, E-CONCIERGE AI will also offer AI-enhanced technical support, guiding technicians through complex tasks and providing real-time solutions, equipping them to solve issues more swiftly and accurately. Our mission is more than just improving efficiency; we aim to revolutionize the experience for both customers and service providers. We envision a future where home services are reliable, effective, and user-friendly, and we are eager to lead the way in this transformative journey.

column9: Always know what's happening with your servers. IfMetrics monitor your Unix system with all running processes. When we find an error our state-of-art AI will automagically fix it. PROACTIVE IfMetrics is an AI-powered tool that monitors your Unix system in realtime. It comes with a state-of-art AI, which helps you detect problems and irregularities on your system. Unlike other monitoring tools IfMetrics will automagically fix problems that are deemed to be harmful to your server. It is able to self-learn using concepts of self-supervised machine learning. It gives you the power of fixing your system yourself without ever having to contact a support person or engineer. PREDICT HEALTH You can use IfMetrics to monitor daemon processes or similar programs running on localhost. IfMetrics is particularly useful for monitoring daemon processes, such as those started at system boot time from /etc/init/ For instance sendmail, sshd, apache and mysql. FILES, DIRS AND FILESYSTEMS You can also use IfMetrics to monitor files, directories and filesystems on localhost. IfMetrics can monitor these items for changes, such as timestamps changes, checksum changes or size changes. This is also useful for security reasons - you can monitor the md5 or sha1 checksum of files that should not change and get an alert or perform an action if they should change.

But new developments in Graph Databases and cloud computing have made Knowledge Graphs a practical reality. We've decided that ThinkBase is our future, so we've made all the different elements of the DARL ecosystem available in a single Knowledge Graph model. With ThinkBase you can: Integrate your organization's specialized knowledge of the structures and relationships that make up your business. Weaponize that by building in Fuzzy expert system rules to make it an active reasoning engine Use common sense reasoning to make inferences and perform sanity checks. Communicate with your reasoning engine using a fully configurable ChatBot front end.

column9: AI and the future of Payment Technology Adroit Partners invests in merchant portfolios that can take advantage of future AI payment technology, like Computer and voice activated payments.  Computer-vision powered payments Utilizing AI in the payments space has streamlined the functionality of payment technology.  As more consumers shop online and via mobile, facial recognition has been a more recent technology that many see as the future of digital payments.  By using device-vision AI, credit and debit card data can be stored with your facial ID and used to make purchases.   Amazon’s Deeplens technology which enables cameras to check out your grocery items without going through a cashier is one example of this.  While it’s still in development, it’s set to disrupt payment systems. Voice-activated payments Biometric protected payments are now more mainstream as they integrate with most smartphones. But more advancements are aspiring to integrate AI powered smart assistants with voice-recognition technologies. With voice-activated payment technology, smart assistants access your accounts for the transaction. In the future, voice activated payments won’t be hinged on assistants or other biometric securities for verification. As effortless payment leads the way in the digital transformation of financial services,  it won’t take long before these displace the current methods used today.

column9: We are physicians who code, so that provides us with a unique perspective in building our platform. As practicing physicians, each day we see the limits and failings of existing EMR systems. Those systems have demonstrated that they are incapable of scale. They impose artificial patient capacity limits on physicians and represent a contributing source of physician burnout. As a result, healthcare has outgrown its current technology and patient care suffers.  Our mission is to change this with Artificial Intelligence. And with that, to create a paradigm shift in patient care, allowing physicians and healers to contribute knowledge and leverage the latest innovations in AI technology to develop an intelligent patient outcome feedback loop.  Our AI model has been specifically designed to accelerate the advancement of clinical therapies and expand the reach and impact of these advancements. This will permit medicine to bring to reality the dream of equity inpatient care by accruing and sharing physicians’ cumulative discoveries, knowledge, and experiences with every single patient encounter. To accomplish this, we have built the foundation of our company on passion, care, and most importantly, re-imaging what is possible through creative Artificial Intelligence innovations applied to medical care.
